  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 10th level, you've gained the ability to come up with solutions under pressure. </p><p>When you or another creature you can see within 30 feet of you makes a Skill check or a saving throw, you can use your reaction to add your Intelligence modifier to the roll. </p><p>At Level 15, you also use this feature to subtract your Intelligence Modifier from an enemy creature's Skill check or saving throw. </p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier (minimum of once). </p><p>You regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>",
